{"tid":227894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那訂立國歌法：不尊重國歌、噓國歌現象將受規管","createTime":"2017-05-03T13:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T04:32:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b7771174eef7446b9c254c2d67fc66cb404348f","tid":227894,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/中國擬訂立國歌法-原解放軍樂團長-不尊重國歌-噓國歌現象將受規管/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E8%A8%82%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%B3%95-%E5%8E%9F%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%A8%82%E5%9C%98%E9%95%B7-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C-%E5%99%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E7%8F%BE%E8%B1%A1%E5%B0%87%E5%8F%97%E8%A6%8F%E7%AE%A1%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2Bcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3fbf017d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E8%A8%82%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%B3%95-%E5%8E%9F%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%A8%82%E5%9C%98%E9%95%B7-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C-%E5%99%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E7%8F%BE%E8%B1%A1%E5%B0%87%E5%8F%97%E8%A6%8F%E7%AE%A1%2F&h=c4c79248\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/中國擬訂立國歌法-原解放軍樂團長-不尊重國歌-噓國歌現象將受規管/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/2_0BJDi_1200x0.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F2_0BJDi_1200x0.PNG&h=3f908e60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那人大網昨日公佈了「全支那人大常委會2017年立法工作計劃」，其中包括支那國歌法，並擬於今年6月初審。已經連續十年提案倡支那國歌立法的全支那國政協、原匪軍軍樂團團長于海，接受北京青年網訪問時表示，現在社會上對支那國歌不尊重、褻瀆甚至侮辱的現象非常多，支那國歌被一些人篡改為二奶歌，甚至出現在公開場合「噓國歌」的現象，故此有必要立法保護支那國歌。<br />\n<br />\n于海認為，支那國歌法應主要講一些原則性的規定，比如支那國歌面前公民表現對國家、民族的熱愛，讓唱好支那國歌成為公民的一個基本要求。其立法重點是說在正式場合下，對支那國歌要敬畏，這是對支那族的尊重；在公開場合下，演奏支那國歌應該有一個參照，使用正確的版本演奏；在重大場合下，支那國歌在演奏演唱時應該被尊重，故此個人唱不好國歌並不就是違法。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，目前支那國歌版本比較混亂，一些存在錯誤的樂譜還在使用，亦有版本不統一的情況，故支那國歌法應統一支那國歌標準。<br />\n<br />\n于海又表示，外國的國歌法規定，在公開場合下羞辱國歌是要受到懲罰的，比如一個羅馬尼亞歌手在公開場合篡改國歌就被判刑罰款。他認為，支那國歌作為支那國家形象，不允許有任何的失誤。"},{"pid":"383db5d0267fbcf3fa9c6cc4d6ca9e9a74e4c7b4","tid":227894,"uid":90863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"邊個政黨拉國歌作詞人去批鬥？"},{"pid":"c39f74c0e4485d89e8b80cd185a6e0242d7b5b10","tid":227894,"uid":35860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個政黨拉國歌作詞人去批鬥？</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d338ba288411e60cba7d581966a39b5ad2335d","tid":227894,"uid":37413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"咁神聖想問作國歌條友有咩下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d713416e03d48113da950784e3deb01576b9b3a","tid":227894,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁神聖想問作國歌條友有咩下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫咩名？"},{"pid":"96de4c39768d004fe90cd08849e313f38e77fed2","tid":227894,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁神聖想問作國歌條友有咩下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9269accd3acfdc0bf3817a03cd46d0dd1eeb4a8","tid":227894,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁神聖想問作國歌條友有咩下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只係歷史洪流既沙沙石石"},{"pid":"69379742a1172ad5c89b122600ca8200